snippet.title: Island Cities - Steam release trailer
snippet.description:
Arrange the town islands and see them come to life. Just swap the blocks of a 3D jigsaw puzzle.

Island Cities is available on Steam for PC and Mac
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2093900/Island_Cities__Jigsaw_Puzzle/

Developed by Mens Sana Interactive
Music by Tatyana Jacques
